location.fullValue: BONITA NATIONAL GOLF AND COUNTRY CLUB

data.description: Welcome to this charming 2 bedroom, 2 bath home located in the desirable Bonita Springs, Florida. This cozy home boasts a spacious living area, a well-appointed kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and a screened-in lanai perfect for enjoying the beautiful Florida weather. The master suite features a private en-suite bathroom and ample closet space. The second bedroom is perfect for guests or use as a home office. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and the stunning beaches of the Gulf of Mexico, this home is a must-see!
